---
title: Gravy Bacon, Beef & Pork Filo Pie with Veggies & Cheddar Cheese
description: This pie needs to be on a picture-perfect windowsill, with singing birds in the background. The rich gravy beef and pork filling will lull you into a calm atmosphere and the roasted root veggies adds a crisp finishin touch.
